## ðŸ”§ Common `gcloud` Commands and Their Purpose

| Command | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `gcloud auth list` | Shows which account is currently active |
| `gcloud config list` | Displays your current project, region, and zone |
| `gcloud config set project [PROJECT_ID]` | Switches your focus to a specific project |
| `gcloud info` | Provides a big-picture summary of your current Cloud SDK setup |
